text: Nevzat Güzelırmak (1 January 1942 – 12 October 2020) was a Turkish football defender and later manager. He played 18 times for Turkey from 1962 to 1968. He also played for Göztepe S.K. between 1960 to 1975. Güzelırmak died on 12 October 2020 at the age of 78. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Turkish footballers Category:Turkish football managers
